Alan Knill can motivate Torquay, says Gulls chief
Media playback is not supported on this deviceTorquay chairman Thea Bristow tells BBC South West that Alan Knill can motivate the club in a positive way next season.Martin Ling was replaced this week by Knill, who has been in interim charge of the side while Ling recovered from illness.